{"tid":2043546,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"1997＋23=2047 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-05-30T13:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T13:29:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4920c1dbe9aa59731412db9b0b5d374e8f517755","tid":2043546,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200530/20927383/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200530%2F20927383%2F&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD1lQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=e51acc04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200530%2F20927383%2F&h=dc98f130\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200530/20927383/</a><br />\n<br />\n1997＋23=2047 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200530/large/1590735358_5531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200530%2Flarge%2F1590735358_5531.jpg&h=9792c564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「527大圍捕」，警察共拘捕396人，其中180人為學生，80人未成年。結果警署外家長雲集，有等候保釋子女的，有在返工前特意來送早餐給孩子的。有家長向記者展示早餐，並非精心炮製的美食，只是順手從家中拿來的麵包，旨在讓孩子安心，讓孩子知道家長支持他。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n真是可憐天下父母心。<br />\n<br />\n「528」塵埃落定之後，有網民在網絡發文指：「事到如今，我認為我人生最了不起的成就就是不生孩子。」把孩子帶來亂世，如何教育他／她，面臨重大抉擇，或教會他／她麻木，讓他／她苟安於世，成為沒有靈魂的人；或讓他／她擁有高貴的靈魂，而你每天為他／她的安危操碎了心。無論哪一種選擇，都是痛苦的。而總有一天，家長會比孩子早一步離開塵世，把孩子留在這樣一個亂世中，於心何忍？<br />\n<br />\n那個「事到如今」。。。。。。。。。不禁一額冷汗。<br />\n<br />\n可是，這些未成年孩子們，在十幾年前出世，那時候，他們的家長可沒想過1997加23等於2047。他們當時決定生孩子，又有甚麼錯？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afc3faee80797c374c6538281b6b729cda255c2","tid":2043546,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"我睇到個標題<br />\n高慧然點解=27?<br />\n<br />\n睇左內文先明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}